A strike!

620
01:04:11,806 --> 01:04:13,274
Two outs.

621
01:04:39,376 --> 01:04:41,424
What are you guys waiting for?
Let's go!

622
01:04:42,796 --> 01:04:45,049
Come on, rebound the ball.
Move it!

623
