640
01:08:14,799 --> 01:08:18,099
I'm nice too. Just like the boy.

641
01:08:20,513 --> 01:08:22,607
I see.

642
01:08:23,141 --> 01:08:28,113
I'm not ashamed to say that I
could use a drink about now. Oh.

643
