It's no trouble at all.
Why don't you take mine?

666
01:10:11,207 --> 01:10:13,005
Thank you.

667
01:10:17,839 --> 01:10:19,933
So like I was saying,

668
01:10:20,717 --> 01:10:24,221
I worked as an independent.

669
