678
01:11:52,225 --> 01:11:54,398
Do you mind?

679
01:11:55,645 --> 01:11:59,070
No, not at all.

680
01:12:10,159 --> 01:12:11,911
You know,
maybe in the morning,

681
01:12:12,078 --> 01:12:16,049
