Maybe even 20.

684
01:12:24,048 --> 01:12:26,267
Perhaps, we shall see.

685
01:12:27,009 --> 01:12:29,603
You can relax. I've done this before.

686
01:12:30,596 --> 01:12:31,768
That's all right.

687
